    public class CheckboxesTag
extends AbstractMultiCheckedElementTag
    The <checkboxes> tag renders multiple HTML 'input' tags with type 'checkbox'. Intended to be used with a Collection as the AbstractMultiCheckedElementTag.getItems() bound value.
